<recipe>
<title>
Birthday Cake Popcorn Recipe
</title>
<details>
PREP TIME: 10 minutes
COOK TIME: 5 minutes
TOTAL TIME: 15 minutes
</details>
<ingredients>
3 oz package natural microwave popcorn
12 oz . package vanilla chips
2 T . coconut oil
1 oz nonpareils
</ingredients>
<instructions>
Microwave popcorn according to package directions.
Meanwhile, add vanilla chips and coconut oil to heavy saucepan.
Cook over low heat until melted, stirring regularly.
Add cooked popcorn to large bowl.
Pour in melted vanilla chip mixture, and toss popcorn to coat.
Spread coated popcorn on waxed or parchment paper.
Sprinkle with nonpareils right away.
Let cool to set.
Gently break into pieces, and enjoy!
This popcorn is best enjoyed the same day it's made.
</instructions>
</recipe>
